a4 \uc6d4\ub4dc \ub808\ucf54\ub4dc\uc640 \ud568\uaed8 \uc138\uacc4 3\ub300 \uae30\ub85d\uc778\uc99d \ucd9c\ubc94|date=7 October 2017|accessdate=10 November 2017|publisher=Supertalent World Record News}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.ilbe.com/10113383494|title=\uad6d\ub0b4 \uccab \uc138\uacc4\uae30\ub124\uc2a4 \uae30\uad6c \uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uc6d4\ub4dc\ub808\ucf54\ub4dc \ucc3d\ub9bd, \uc778\uc99d\ud589\uc0ac \uc131\ud669\ub9ac \ub05d\ub098|date=30 October 2017|accessdate=10 November 2017|publisher=ilbe news}}</ref>\n\n==Titleholders==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- \n!width=\"10\"|Year||width=\"150\"|Country||width=\"150\"|Name||width=\"30\"|Age {{ref label|note01|A|}}  ||width=\"30\"|Height||width=\"80\"|Hometown||width=\"200\"|Pageant venue & date||width=\"100\"|Number of Entrants\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | 2019\n| {{Flag|France}}\n| Myriam Cassim <ref>{{cite news|title=Mayotte: Myriam Cassim est \u00e9lue Miss Super ... - Comores|url=http://comores.niooz.fr/mayotte-myriam-cassim-est-elue-miss-super-talent-2020-a-rome-33559789.shtml|publisher=Comores Infos=2 November 2019|accessdate=4 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 24\n| 5'10\"\n| [[Mayotte]]\n| '''Rome Cavalieri [[Waldorf Astoria Hotels & Resorts]]''' 2 November\n| 105+\n|-\n| {{Flag|Russia}}\n| [[Lada Akimova]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Russian model determines on working in Korea because of BTS|url=https://channels.vlive.tv/B5F927/vtoday/1.11685581|publisher=vlive.tv=16 August 2019|accessdate=4 November 2019}}</ref>\n| 21\n| 5'8\"\n| [[Moscow]]\n| '''Seoul Dragon City''' 10 May\n| 94\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | 2018\n| {{Flag|Netherlands}}\n| Ekaterina Ksenzova<ref>{{cite news|title=\uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uc6b0\uc2b9 \uc5d0\uce74\ud14c\ub9ac\ub098 \uc13c\ucd08\ubc14, \"\ub808\ub4dc\ubca8\ubcb3\uac19\uc740 \u97d3\uac78\uadf8\ub8f9 \ub418\uace0\ud30c\"|url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news/read/700738|publisher=Retail News|date=13 November 2018|accessdate=13 November 2018}}</ref>\n| 18\n| 5'10\"\n| [[Overi