 = [[Suta Group]]\n| website               = {{URL|http://supertalent.co}}\n}}\n\nThe '''Miss Supertalent of the World''' is a twice-yearly high-profile media event operated by [[Suta Group]] participating fashion stars of beauty queen, supermodel, actress, pop artists, host, dance champion with unique format showcasing fashion and talent. Supertalent [[Fashion Week]] and Supertalent [[World Record]] are units of Miss Supertalent preliminary, it was held [[Seoul]], [[Busan]], [[Daegu]] in Asia to [[Paris]], [[Nice]], [[Milan]], [[Rome]] in Europe.<ref>{{cite news|title=2016\ub144 \ubbf8\uc2a4 \uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uacb8 \uc138\uacc4 \ubcfc\ub8f8\ub304\uc2a4 \ucc54\ud504 \ub098\ud0c8\ub9ac \ubc14\uccb8\ucf54, \uac00\uc218\ub85c \ub370\ubdd4! |url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news/read/719297 |publisher=Sports Seoul News|date=11 January 2019 |accessdate=25 January 2019}}</ref> .<ref>{{cite news|title=50 Global Superstars To Compete in Miss SuperTalent of the World 2016|url=http://www.retailnews.asia/50-global-superstars-to-compete-in-miss-supertalent-of-the-world-2016/|publisher=Retail News|date=27 February 2016|accessdate=8 December 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Milett Figueroa se corona Miss Supertalent of the World 2016|url=http://rpp.pe/famosos/chollywood/milett-figueroa-se-corona-miss-supertalent-of-the-world-2016-noticia-1014145/|publisher=RPP|date=3 December 2016|accessdate=8 December 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Natalie Stejskalova wins Miss Supertalent World 2016|url=http://beautypageants.indiatimes.com/others/Natalie-Stejskalova-wins-Miss-Supertalent-World-2016/articleshow/52277576.cms|work=The Times of India|date=15 March 2016|accessdate=8 December 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Miss Supertalent 2016: Milett Figueroa recibe duras cr\u00edticas por desafinar|url=http://www.americatv.com.pe/noticias/espectaculos/miss-supertalent-2016-milett-figueroa-recibe-duras-criticas-desafinar-n256756|publisher=America TV|date=5 December 2016|access