ris, which was first time in Eiffel Tower its kind of showcase.<ref>{{cite news|title=\uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uc6b0\uc2b9 \uc5d0\uce74\ud14c\ub9ac\ub098 \uc13c\ucd08\ubc14, \"\ub808\ub4dc\ubca8\ubcb3\uac19\uc740 \u97d3\uac78\uadf8\ub8f9 \ub418\uace0\ud30c\n|url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news/read/700738 |publisher=Sports Seoul News|date=13 November 2019 |accessdate=25 January 2019}}</ref> Season 13 was showcasing the 34 European cities in 20 days-long from France to Italy and final was to be held [[Rome]] Cavalieri [[Waldorf Astoria Hotels & Resorts]] on 2 November<ref>{{cite news|title=Super talent of the World Season 13/2019\n|url=https://en.dailymail24.com/2019/10/28/super-talent-of-the-world-seaso/ |publisher=Daily Mail 24 l News|date=28 October 2019 |accessdate=30 November 2019}}</ref>\n\nNotable past contestants include [[Meriam George]], [[Milett Figueroa]],<ref>{{cite news|title=\uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uc2dc\uc98c7 \uc131\ub8cc\u2026 \ud398\ub8e8 \ud53c\uac8c\ub85c\uc544\u00b7\uccb4\ucf54 \ud3a0\uc694\ubc14 \uacf5\ub3d9\uc6b0\uc2b9\n|url=http://moneys.mt.co.kr/news/mwView.php?type=1&no=2016120810508042578&outlink=1 |publisher=Money Today News|date=8 December 2016 |accessdate=25 January 2019}}</ref> [[Anna Lundh]], [[Diana Arno]],<ref>{{cite news|title=\uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \ucd9c\uc2e0 \ub2e4\uc774\uc544\ub098 \uc544\ub974\ub178, \uc5d0\uc2a4\ud1a0\ub2c8\uc544 \ucd5c\uace0\uc758 \ud328\uc158 \ub514\uc790\uc774\ub108\ub85c \uc120\uc815\ub3fc |url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news/read/717632 |publisher=Sports Seoul News|date=7 January 2019 |accessdate=25 January 2019}}</ref> [[Maria Sten]], [[Dipna Patel]], [[Malina Joshi]]. [[Lada Akimova]]\n\n==''Supertalent Fashion Week''==\nMiss Supertalent Organization had launched a series of spin-off shows 'Supertalent [[Fashion Week]]' which showed the clips of Miss Supertalent Contestants's Fashion Week from all over the world. The event is three days long per season and held twice a year at the [[Korea International Exhibition Center]], [[Daegu]] Textile Complex, [[Incheon International Airport]],<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.stardailynews.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=146093|title=\uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8, \uc624\ub298\uc740 \ud328\uc158\ubaa8\ub378 '\ud0a8\ud14d\uc2a4 \ud328\uc158\uc1fc'|date=12 May 2017|work=Star Daily|accessdate=10 November 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.e2news.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=102707|title=\uc544\ubc14\ud0c0TV '\ubbf8\uc2a4 \uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 2017' \ud604\uc7a5 \uc0dd\uc911\uacc4|date=12 October 2017|accessdate=10 November 2017|publisher=e2news}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newsis.com/view/?id=NISX20171020_0000123684&cID=10810&pID=10800|title=[\ub300\uad6c\uc18c\uc2dd]\ub300\uad6c\ub3c4\uc2dc\ucca0\ub3c4, \ub514\ud2b8\ub85c \ud328\uc158\uc1fc \uac1c\ucd5c \ub4f1|date=21 October 2017|accessdate=10 November 2017|publisher=Newsis}}</ref> [[South Korea]], [[Eiffel Tower]], [[Galeries Lafayette]],<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news/read/699670|title=\uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uc2dc\uc98c 11, \ub77c\ud30c\uc5d0\ud2b8 \uac24\ub7ec\ub9ac\uc640 \ud30c\ub9ac \uc624\ud398\ub77c\uc88c\ub97c \ub354\uc6b1 \ub208\ubd80\uc2dc\uac8c~|accessdate=10 November 2018|publisher=Sports Seoul=10 November 2018}}</ref> Paris, [[Jungfrau]],<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news/read/697515|title=\uc54c\ud504\uc2a4\uc758 \ube44\uacbd \uc735\ud504\ub77c\uc6b0\uc5d0\uc11c \ud328\uc158\uc1fc\ub97c \ud3bc\uce5c \uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \ucc38\uac00\uc790\ub4e4, \uc544\uc774\uac70 \uc55e\uc5d0\uc11c \uc2e0\uace0\uc2dd\uc744~|accessdate=12 November 2018|publisher=Sports Seoul=5 November 2018}}</ref> [[Schilthorn]],<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sportsseoul.com/news/read/697888|title=\uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uc2dc\uc98c 11, \uc54c\ud504\uc2a4\ub97c \ub7f0\uc6e8\uc774\ub85c \ub9cc\ub4e4\uc5b4\ubc84\ub824~|accessdate=12 November 2018|publisher=Sports Seoul=6 November 2018}}</ref> [[Switzerland]]\n\n==''Supertalent World Record''==\nMiss Supertalent Organization in collaboration with Challenge Korea Headquarters had launched Supertalent World Record which is world's authority on record-breaking achievements to best global performance ever recorded and officially verified in a specific skills and human achievement of entertainment, sports, politician and 4th industrial entertainment solutions. [[Psy]], [[Ban Ki-moon]], [[Song Hae]], [[Hong Soo-hwan]], [[Jin Yong]], [[Cho Yong-pil]], [[Park Chan-ho]], [[Lee Seung-yuop]], [[Jang Mi-ran]], [[Cho Yong-pil]] and other winners were awarded Supertalent World Record.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.g-enews.com/view.php?ud=201710122122257534c4c55f9b3d_1&md=20171012214346_I|title='\ubbf8\uc2a4 \uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ub4dc \uc2dc\uc98c9' 13\uc77c \ud55c\uad6d\uc11c \uac1c\ub9c9\u2026\uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uc6d4\ub4dc \ub808\ucf54\ub4dc \uc778\uc99d|date=13 October 2017|accessdate=10 November 2017|publisher=Global Economic News}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://sworldrecord.com/37|title='\uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uc6d4\ub4dc \ub808\ucf54\ub4dc'\ub97c \uac1c\ucd5c \uae30\ub124\uc2a4 \uc6d4\ub4dc \ub808\ucf54\ub4dc\uc640 \ud568\uaed8 \uc138\uacc4 3\ub300 \uae30\ub85d\uc778\uc99d \ucd9c\ubc94|date=7 October 2017|accessdate=10 November 2017|publisher=Supertalent World Record News}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.ilbe.com/10113383494|title=\uad6d\ub0b4 \uccab \uc138\uacc4\uae30\ub124\uc2a4 \uae30\uad6c \uc288\ud37c\ud0e4\ub7f0\ud2b8 \uc6d4\ub4dc\ub808\ucf54\ub4dc \ucc3d\ub9bd, \uc778\uc99d\ud589\uc0ac \uc131\ud669\ub9ac \ub05d\ub098|date=30 October 2017|accessdate=10 November 2017|publisher=ilbe news}}</ref>\n\n==Titleholders==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- \n!width=\"10\"|Year||width=\"150\"|Country||width=\"150\"|Name||width=\"30\"|Age {{ref label|note01|A|}}  ||width=\"30\"|Height||width=\"80\"|Hometown||width=\"200\"|Pageant venue & date||width=\"100\"|Nu